Review_Text: Why call it "Coastal Britain" when it only includes a small part of the British coastline that is found in England. Scotland alone has a longer coastline than England and if you add Wales and Ireland England palls into insignificance.

I never really believe that Kate Humble is as down to earth as she claims, or half as interested in what she is apparently passionate about in programmes such as this.But this remains an interesting enough programme, and passes the time for many I'm sure.I wouldn't watch again though.
